description.narrative: This activity covers the resourcing requirements to design the Scholarships Programme as a result of the Scholarships Improvements Project which will run from 2019 - 2021 or beyond in its implementation phase. The improvements project includes building an enhanced scholarships model; ensuring our policies, systems and processes support efficient delivery of the New Zealand Scholarships Programme; and improving monitoring and evaluation.
